western Europe-bound natural gas pipelines through Ukraine if the
problem of Ukraine's unauthorized skimming of Russian gas is
settled.
</P>
<P>
Russia will also help finish the construction of the Ronvno and
Khmelnitsky nuclear power plants in Ukraine, Kasyanov said.
</P>
<P>
The Russian Black Sea fleet's arrears in infrastructure
payments to Ukraine and Kiev's gas debt of 1.9 billion U.S.dollars
to Russia have long hampered their bilateral ties and economic and
trade cooperation. 
</P>
