<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, July 19 (Xinhua) -- The European Union (EU) adopted a
proposal Wednesday on the opening of negotiations for a
Stabilizaton and Association Agreement with the Republic of
Croatia.
</P>
<P>
