Harvey of the Red Deer Fire Department announced the official end
of the search for bodies in Pine Lake.
</P>
<P>
Officials say 11 people were killed and 140 others were sent to
hospital after tornado touched down at about 07:30 p.m. (0030 GMT)
at the speed of 300 kilometers an hour, cutting through the Green
Acre campground until it tapered off across the lake more than 20
kilometers away.
</P>
<P>
