climbed to 2000 points. However, they were still concerned and
wanted to take profits, as the index was on the historical high
level.
</P>
<P>
Some ST shares, mutual funds and the shares held by the mutual
funds performed actively. The good performance of H shares may be
related to positive news about H share development, said Homeway.
</P>
