<HEADLINE> Shanghai Opens Highway Transport Service Website </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 19 (Xinhua) -- The transport system in Shanghai,
China's biggest industrial and trade center, recently opened its
first highway transport service website.
</P>
<P>
The website embraced more than 20 service items, including
information inquiry and cargo exchange.
</P>
<P>
Getting access to the website, passengers may acquire the
schedule of coaches transport, and cargo businessmen can also get
information of transport prices.
