<P>
BRUSSELS -- The European Union (EU) believed it won a victory
Tuesday in banana trade war over the United States after the World
Trade Organization (WTO) ruled that U.S. sanctions worth 191
million U.S. dollars were imposed prematurely.
</P>
<P>
