WASHINGTON -- The Multilateral Investment Fund (MIF) announced
Tuesday the approval of 15.3 million U.S. dollars in credit and
grants to support small business and microenterprise,
environmental protection, and regulatory reform in Latin America
and the Caribbean. (MIF-S.America-Credit)
</P>
