Democratic Front (ADF) in the jungles of Mount Rwenzori in western
Uganda and eastern Democratic Republic of the Congo, the New
Vision daily reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
"We have taken over all the fourteen locations of the ADF in
the mountain and we are searching for unknown ones," UPDF Second
Division Commander Fred Tolit was quoted as saying.
</P>
