shall defeat them on the battle field," he said.
</P>
<P>
Ugandan President Yoweri Museveni has given an amnesty to all
rebel groups fighting the government. The Amnesty Act, which
expired on Tuesday, has been extended for another six months,
according to the Ugandan Amnesty Commission. 
